Mɛi ni woɔ mɛi ni agbo yɛ amɛnɔ lɛ ŋaa lɛ ateŋ mɛi komɛi woɔ mɛi ni ewa kɛhã amɛ akɛ amɛaakpee awerɛhoyeli naa lɛ ŋaa ni amɛfee nibii kɛye amɛbua mɛi krokomɛi loo ni amɛkɛ amɛbe aye abua kɛtsu maŋ nitsumɔ ko .
Enɛ baanyɛ ahã mɔ lɛ aná miishɛɛ , ni ebaaba ewerɛhoyeli lɛ shi .
Kristofoi babaoo ni agbo yɛ amɛnɔ lɛ ena akɛ , mɛi krokomɛi ní amɛyeɔ amɛbuaa lɛ shɛjeɔ amɛmii . ​ — 2 Korintobii 1 : 3 , 4 .
Kɛ́ oopiŋ lɛ , Nyɔŋmɔ nuɔ he ehãa bo . — Lala 55 : 23 ; 1 Petro 5 : 7 .
Nyɔŋmɔ boɔ etsuji asɔlemɔ toi . — Lala 86 : 5 ; 1 Tesalonikabii 5 : 17 .
Nyɔŋmɔ hiɛ tseɔ mɛi ni egboi . — Hiob 14 : 13 - 15 .
Nyɔŋmɔ ewo shi akɛ ebaatee mɛi ni egboi lɛ ashi . ​ — Yesaia 26 : 19 ; Yohane 5 : 28 , 29 .
Ani onaanyo ko suɔlɔ egbo ni onaaa bɔ ni obaafee oshɛje emii pɛŋ ?
Bei komɛi lɛ wɔleee nɔ ni wɔbaakɛɛ loo nɔ ni wɔbaafee ​ — no hewɔ lɛ wɔfeee nɔ ko nɔ ko .
Shi nibii komɛi yɛ ni wɔbaanyɛ wɔfee kɛye wɔbua .
Bei pii lɛ , nɔ ni nɔŋŋ ni he hiaa ji ní obaahi emasɛi , ni okɛɛ lɛ nɔ ko tamɔ , “ Edɔ mi waa , kpoo onu . ”
Yɛ maji pii anɔ lɛ , fuamɔ ni obaafua mɔ lɛ loo enine mli ni obaamɔ kɛkɛ po hãa enuɔ he akɛ osusuɔ ehe .
Kɛ́ mɔ ni agbo yɛ enɔ lɛ miitao ni ewie lɛ , bo lɛ toi jogbaŋŋ .
Nɔ ni fe fɛɛ lɛ , obaanyɛ ofee nibii komɛi ni weku ni agbo yɛ amɛnɔ lɛ nyɛko afee lɛ ohã amɛ , tamɔ nihoomɔ , gbekɛbii lɛ akwɛmɔ , loo obaanyɛ oye obua kɛto yara lɛ he gbɛjianɔ kɛ́ amɛmiisumɔ .
Nibii ni tamɔ enɛɛmɛi lɛ baaye abua mɛi ni agbo yɛ amɛnɔ lɛ kwraa fe wiemɔi ni ŋɔɔ ni obaawie .
Sɛɛ mli lɛ , obaanyɛ owie mɔ ni egbo lɛ he saji komɛi , tamɔ ekolɛ esui kpakpai komɛi loo nibii komɛi ni efee ni yɔɔ miishɛɛ lɛ ahe .
Ekolɛ saji ni tamɔ nɛkɛ lɛ baahã mɔ ni agbo yɛ enɔ lɛ aŋmɔ po .
Akɛ nɔkwɛmɔnɔ lɛ , yoo ko ni atsɛɔ lɛ Pam , ni ewu ni atsɛɔ lɛ Ian lɛ gbo afii ekpaa nɛ lɛ kɛɛ akɛ : “ Bei komɛi lɛ mɛi kɛɔ mi nibii kpakpai ni Ian fee ehã amɛ ni milé po , ni enɛ hãa mináa miishɛɛ . ”
Akpa shi ana akɛ , kɛ́ agbo yɛ mɔ ko nɔ lɛ , amrɔ nɔŋŋ lɛ enanemɛi yeɔ amɛbua lɛ , shi be ni be shwieɔ mli lɛ , hiɛ kpaa enɔ .
No hewɔ lɛ , kɛfee oti ni ma ohiɛ akɛ , kɛ́ agbo yɛ onaanyo ko nɔ lɛ , obaafɔ eshi bimɔ .
* Mɛi ni agbo yɛ amɛnɔ lɛ ateŋ mɛi pii ahiɛ sɔɔ enɛ waa , ejaakɛ eyeɔ ebuaa amɛ ni amɛkpeɔ amɛwerɛhoyeli lɛ naa .
Susumɔ yoo ko ni jɛ Japan ni atsɛɔ lɛ Kaori , ni hao waa be ni enyɛmi yoo nukpa gbo nyɔji 15 enumɔ yɛ emami gbele sɛɛ lɛ niiashikpamɔ lɛ he okwɛ .
Miishɛɛ sane ji akɛ , enanemɛi lɛ tee nɔ amɛye amɛbua lɛ .
Kaori naanyo ko ni atsɛɔ lɛ Ritsuko lɛ ye lɛ onukpa kwraa , shi yoo nɛɛ ŋɔ lɛ efee enaanyo .
Kaori kɛɛ akɛ : “ Yɛ anɔkwale mli lɛ , kulɛ minyaaa he .
Ejaakɛ misumɔɔɔ ni mikɛ mɔ ko yeɔ mimami najiaŋ , ni misusuuu akɛ mɔ ko baanyɛ efee nibii ni mimami feɔ ehãa mi lɛ ehã mi .
Shi bɔ ni Mama Ritsuko kɛ mi ye ehã lɛ hã naanyobɔɔ ni yɔɔ gbagbalii bakã mi kɛ lɛ teŋ .
Daa otsi lɛ , mi kɛ lɛ feɔ ekome kɛyaa shiɛmɔ kɛ Kristofoi akpeei .
Efɔ̃ɔ mi nine ni mi kɛ lɛ yanuɔ tii , ebahãa mi niyenii , ni eŋmalaa mi woji , ni ekɛ kaadi majeɔ mi .
Nibii kpakpai ni Mama Ritsuko fee lɛ ná minɔ hewalɛ waa . ”
Ní Kaori mami gbo nɛɛ , afii 12 eho , ni amrɔ nɛɛ , lɛ kɛ ewu fɛɛ kɛ amɛbe fɛɛ miishiɛ .
Kaori kɛɛ akɛ : “ Mama Ritsuko miiya nɔ eefee nibii kɛmiitsɔɔ akɛ esusuɔ mihe lolo .
Be fɛɛ be ni maku misɛɛ maya shĩa lɛ , miyasaraa lɛ , ni ewoɔ mi hewalɛ waa , ni enɛ hãa mináa miishɛɛ . ”
Mɔ kroko hu ni mɛi tee nɔ amɛye amɛbua lɛ be ni agbo yɛ enɔ lɛ ji Yehowa Odasefonyo ko ni yɔɔ Cyprus ni atsɛɔ lɛ Poli lɛ .
Bei pii lɛ efɔ̃ɔ awusãi kɛ okulafoi nine kɛbaa amɛshĩa lɛ ni amɛkɛ amɛ gbaa sane ni amɛkɛ amɛyeɔ nii , ni enɛ ji nɔkwɛmɔnɔ ni sa waa .
Dɔlɛ sane ji akɛ , be ni Sozos ná afii 53 lɛ , ená aŋsɔ hela ko , ni egbo .
Be ni amɛyɔɔ jɛmɛ lɛ , amɛkɛ Yehowa Odasefoi asafo ko bɔi bɔɔ .
Poli wie akɛ , “ Mɛi ni yɔɔ wɔsafo hee lɛ mli lɛ lé nɔ ni eba wɔnɔ kɛ naagbai ni wɔkɛkpeɔ .
Shi no etsiii amɛnaa akɛ amɛbaabɛŋkɛ wɔ ni amɛwie nibii ni baashɛje wɔmii ni amɛye amɛbua wɔ .
Yelikɛbuamɔ nɛɛ sa waa , titri lɛ yɛ nakai beiaŋ , ejaakɛ no mli lɛ mibinuu lɛ tsɛ he miihia lɛ waa !
Asafoŋ onukpai lɛ fee nibii ni tsɔɔ akɛ amɛsusuɔ Daniel he waa diɛŋtsɛ .
Amɛteŋ mɔ kome po bɔɔ mɔdɛŋ akɛ be fɛɛ be ni ekɛ enanemɛi baayajie amɛhiɛtserɛ loo amɛbaayatswa bɔɔl lɛ , ebaahã Daniel afata amɛhe . ”
Poli kɛ ebinuu Daniel fɛɛ miiya nɔ jogbaŋŋ ŋmɛnɛ .
Gbɛi srɔtoi pii yɛ ni wɔbaanyɛ wɔtsɔ nɔ wɔshɛje mɛi ni yeɔ awerɛho lɛ amii .
Biblia lɛ hu shɛjeɔ wɔmii kɛtsɔ hiɛnɔkamɔ ni yɔɔ miishɛɛ ni ehãa wɔnáa kɛhã wɔsɛɛ lɛ nɔ .
Mɛi komɛi po kadiɔ gbi ni mɔ lɛ gbo lɛ yɛ amɛkalanda nɔ koni no akai amɛ ni amɛshɛje mɛi ni agbo yɛ amɛ nɔ lɛ amii ​ — yɛ gbi ni mɔ lɛ gbo lɛ nɔ loo yɛ nakai beiaŋ .
Ekolɛ obaakai akɛ , Gail ni atsĩ etã yɛ saji ni tsɔ hiɛ lɛ ateŋ ekome mli lɛ wie akɛ , eleee kɛji ebaanyɛ ekpa ewu Rob gbele lɛ he awerɛho ni eyeɔ lɛ .
Kɛ̃lɛ , eyɛ hiɛnɔkamɔ akɛ ebaana lɛ ekoŋŋ yɛ jeŋ hee ni Nyɔŋmɔ ewo shi akɛ ekɛbaaba lɛ mli .
Minuɔ he waa mihãa mɛi ni suɔlɔi egboi shi amɛbɛ hiɛnɔkamɔ ko kwraa akɛ amɛbaana amɛ ekoŋŋ lɛ . ”
Etsɛŋ , nakai pɛpɛɛpɛ Nyɔŋmɔ baafee ​ — ebaatee Hiob kɛ mɛi babaoo ni anyɛŋ akane lɛ shi ​ — be ni shikpɔŋ lɛ etsɔ paradeiso lɛ .
Biblia wieɔ yɛ Bɔfoi 24 : 15 lɛ akɛ , ‘ Abaatee mɛi ashi . ’
Yesu ma nɔ mi ehã wɔ akɛ , “ Enɛ akafee nyɛ naakpɛɛ ejaakɛ ŋmɛlɛtswaa lɛ miiba , be mli ni mɛi fɛɛ ni yɔɔ gbohii akaimɔ bui lɛ amli lɛ baanu egbee ni amɛbaaje kpo . ”
Ebaaná hegbɛ ‘ etsɔ oblanyo ekoŋŋ ’ ni eheloo lɛ “ aaatsɔ efɔ́ fe gbekɛ nɔ ” kɛya naanɔ .
Nakai nɔŋŋ ebaaji yɛ mɛi fɛɛ ni hiɛ sɔɔ gbɛjianɔ ni Nyɔŋmɔ eto akɛ ebaatee mɛi ashi kɛba wala mli yɛ shikpɔŋ lɛ nɔ lɛ agbɛfaŋ .
Kɛ́ osuɔlɔ ko egbo lɛ , ekolɛ saji ni wɔsusu he kɛtsɔ hiɛ lɛ ejieŋ awerɛho ni oyeɔ lɛ kɛjɛŋ jɛmɛ kwraa .
Shi kɛ́ ojwɛŋ Nyɔŋmɔ shiwoi ni yɔɔ Biblia lɛ mli lɛ anɔ lɛ , obaaná hiɛnɔkamɔ , ni no baaye abua bo ni okpee naa . ​ — 1 Tesalonikabii 4 : 13 .
Ani obaasumɔ ni ole nibii babaoo ni kɔɔ bɔ ni ooofee okpee awerɛhoyeli naa ?
Aloo oyɛ sanebimɔ ko ni kɔɔ sane nɛɛ he , tamɔ “ Mɛni hewɔ Nyɔŋmɔ ŋmɛɔ efɔŋfeemɔ kɛ piŋmɔ gbɛ ? ”
Ofainɛ yaa wɔwɛbsaiti lɛ nɔ , yɛ jw.org / gaa koni okwɛ hetoi ni shɛjeɔ mɔ mii ni Biblia lɛ kɛhãa lɛ .
‘ Nyɔŋmɔ baatsumɔ amɛhiŋmɛiiaŋ yaafonui fɛɛ , ni gbele bɛ dɔŋŋ . ’ ​ — Kpojiemɔ 21 : 3 , 4 .
Buu - Mɔɔ nɛɛ tsɔɔ bɔ ni Nyɔŋmɔ baahã nakai shiwoo lɛ aba mli , kɛ bɔ ni obaaná he sɛɛ .
SANEYITSO LƐ MLITSƆƆMƆ | MƐNI HEWƆ YESU NA AMANEHULU NI EGBO LƐ ?
Yɛ April shishijee mli yɛ afi 33 Ŋ.B . lɛ , agbe Yesu , Nazarenyo lɛ .
Afolɔ enaa akɛ eetse maŋ lɛ hiɛ atua , ayi lɛ musuŋshãa musuŋshãa , ni akala lɛ akpɛtɛ tso he .
Shi Nyɔŋmɔ tee lɛ shi kɛba wala mli ekoŋŋ , ni yɛ gbii 40 sɛɛ lɛ , Yesu tee ŋwɛi .
Wɔnaa sane nɛɛ yɛ Sanekpakpai ejwɛ ni yɔɔ Kristofoi a - Hela Ŋmalɛi , ni afɔɔ lɛ tsɛmɔ akɛ Kpaŋmɔ Hee lɛ mli .
Shi kɛ́ nakai saji lɛ ba lɛɛlɛŋ lɛ , no lɛ adesai baanyɛ akpa shihilɛ kpakpa gbɛ wɔsɛɛ , ni bo hu obaanyɛ oná mli gbɛfaŋnɔ .
No hewɔ lɛ , ani saji ni yɔɔ Sanekpakpai lɛ amli lɛ ji anɔkwa saji aloo adesãi ?
Nɔ ni tamɔɔɔ adesãi ni aka yiŋ aŋmala lɛ , Sanekpakpai lɛ ja , ni amɛyɛ fitsofitso .
Akɛ nɔkwɛmɔnɔ lɛ , atsĩ hei pɔtɛi atã yɛ mli , ni abaanyɛ aya hei nɛɛ babaoo ŋmɛnɛ .
Amɛwieɔ mɛi pɔtɛi ahe , mɛi ni je lɛŋ yinɔsaneŋmalɔi hu ewie amɛhe . ​ — Luka 3 : 1 , 2 , 23 .
Woloŋmalɔi ni hi shi yɛ klɛŋklɛŋ afii 200 lɛ amli lɛ tsĩ Yesu diɛŋtsɛ tã .
* Bɔ ni Sanekpakpai lɛ bɔ gbɛ nɔ ni atsɔ agbe lɛ lɛ he amaniɛ lɛ kɛ bɔ ni Romabii lɛ gbeɔ mɛi yɛ nakai beiaŋ lɛ kpãa gbee .
Kɛfata he lɛ , saji ni abɔ he amaniɛ lɛ ja , ni ashiuuu nɔ ko nɔ ​ — awie nibii komɛi ni Yesu kaselɔi lɛ fee ni esaaa lɛ po he yɛ mli .
Saji nɛɛ fɛɛ maa nɔ mi akɛ mɛi ni ŋma Sanekpakpai lɛ ye anɔkwa , ni nibii ni amɛŋmala yɛ Yesu he lɛ ja .
Eyɛ mli akɛ mɛi babaoo heɔ yeɔ akɛ Yesu hi shi ni egbo moŋ , shi mɛi komɛi baanyɛ aje ŋwane akɛ atee lɛ shi .
Be ni ayabɔ amaniɛ klɛŋklɛŋ kwraa akɛ atee lɛ shi lɛ , ekaselɔi lɛ po heee yeee .
Shi be ni amɛ kɛ mɛi krokomɛi na Yesu yɛ bei srɔtoi amli akɛ atee lɛ shi lɛ , amɛhe amɛye agbɛnɛ .
Anɔkwa sane ji akɛ , yɛ be ko po mli lɛ , mɛi ni fa fe 500 na lɛ . ​ — 1 Korintobii 15 : 6 .
Kaselɔi lɛ jaje Yesu shitee lɛ amɛtsɔɔ mɛi fɛɛ ​ — ní mɛi ni gbe Yesu lɛ hu po fata he ​ — eyɛ mli akɛ no baanyɛ ahã amɔmɔ amɛ ni agbe amɛ .
Eji kaselɔi babaoo nɛɛ bɛ nɔmimaa akɛ atee Yesu shi lɛɛlɛŋ kulɛ , ani amɛbaafee ekãa kɛjaje eshitee lɛ ?
Anɔkwa sane ni eji akɛ atee Yesu shi lɛ ji nɔ ni hã Kristojamɔ ná mɛi anɔ hewalɛ yɛ nakai beiaŋ kɛ ŋmɛnɛ fɛɛ .
Yesu gbele kɛ eshitee lɛ he amaniɛbɔɔ ni yɔɔ Sanekpakpai lɛ amli lɛ ji yinɔsane ni ja jogbaŋŋ .
Kɛ́ okane saji nɛɛ jogbaŋŋ lɛ , obaana faŋŋ akɛ amɛji saji ni ba lɛɛlɛŋ .
Kɛ́ onu nɔ hewɔ ni saji nɛɛ ba lɛ shishi lɛ , hemɔkɛyeli ni oyɔɔ akɛ saji nɛɛ ba lɛɛlɛŋ lɛ mli baawa waa .
Tacitus , ní afɔ lɛ aaafee afii 55 Ŋ.B . lɛ ŋma akɛ , “ Kristus , mɔ mli ni aná gbɛ́i [ Kristofoi ] lɛ kɛjɛ lɛ na amanehulu ni naa wa fe fɛɛ yɛ Tiberio nɔyeli beiaŋ , yɛ wɔ amralofoi lɛ ateŋ mɔ kome , ni ji Pontio Pilato dɛŋ . ”
Mɛi krokomɛi hu ni tsĩ Yesu tã ji Suetonius ( afɔ lɛ afi 69 Ŋ.B . ) ; Yudanyo yinɔsaneŋmalɔ Josephus ( afɔ lɛ afi 37 loo 38 Ŋ.B . ) ; kɛ Pliny the Younger , ni ji Bitinia amralo lɛ ( afɔ lɛ afi 61 loo 62 Ŋ.B . ) .
Agbɛnɛ hu lɛ , enyɛŋ eba akɛ mɛi babaoo ni te shi amɛwo Yesu lɛ baaŋmala saji komɛi ni amɛkɛwo saji ni aŋmala yɛ Yesu he lɛ obɔ ni no ahã mɛi ahe enɔ aye .
Petro , ni ji Yesu bɔfoi lɛ ateŋ mɔ kome lɛ ŋma yɛ Yesu shitee lɛ he akɛ : “ Nyɔŋmɔ tee mɔ nɛ shi yɛ gbi ni ji gbi etɛ lɛ nɔ , ni eŋmɛ lɛ gbɛ ní ejie ehe kpo etsɔɔ faŋŋ , jeee mɛi fɛɛ ejie ehe kpo etsɔɔ lɛ , shi moŋ , ejie ehe kpo etsɔɔ odasefoi ni Nyɔŋmɔ tsɔ hiɛ ehala amɛ eto lɛ , ni ji wɔ , mɛi ni wɔkɛ lɛ ye nii ni wɔkɛ lɛ nu nii , be ni ete shi kɛjɛ gbohii ateŋ lɛ sɛɛ lɛ . ”
Mateo Sanekpakpa lɛ hãa wɔleɔ akɛ , be ni jamɔŋ hiɛnyiɛlɔi ni teɔ shi woɔ Yesu lɛ nu akɛ atee lɛ shi lɛ , amɛtsɔ̃ ŋaa koni mɛi babaoo akanu he . ​ — Mateo 28 : 11 - 15 .
Ani enɛ tsɔɔ akɛ Yesu sumɔɔɔ ni mɛi leɔ akɛ atee lɛ shi ?
Dabi , ejaakɛ Petro wie akɛ : “ Efã wɔ akɛ wɔshiɛ wɔtsɔɔ mɛi lɛ ní wɔye odase fitsofitso akɛ mɔ nɛ ji mɔ ni Nyɔŋmɔ ewo akpɔ akɛ etsɔ hiɛkãalɔi kɛ gbohii akojolɔ lɛ . ”
Anɔkwa Kristofoi lɛ fee nakai , ni amɛkã he amɛmiifee lolo . ​ — Bɔfoi 10 : 42 .
“ Gbɔmɔ kome [ Adam ] nɔ esha tsɔ kɛba je lɛ mli , ni gbele tsɔ esha nɔ kɛba . ” ​ — Romabii 5 : 12
Mɛni obaakɛɛ kɛ́ abi bo akɛ , “ Ani obaasumɔ ni ohi shi kɛya naanɔ ? ”
Ekolɛ mɛi pii baakɛɛ akɛ amɛbaasumɔ , shi amɛsusuɔ akɛ nilee bɛ mli akɛ abaasusu nakai .
Amɛkɛɔ akɛ , mɔ fɛɛ mɔ baagbo , ejaakɛ nakai ji bɔ ni abɔ wɔ .
Shi ŋɔɔ lɛ akɛ , atsɔ sanebimɔ lɛ , ni abi bo akɛ , “ Ani obaasumɔ ni ogbo ? ”
Yɛ anɔkwale mli lɛ , mɛi babaoo baakɛɛ , dabi .
Biblia lɛ tsɔɔ akɛ , Nyɔŋmɔ bɔ wɔ kɛ shwelɛ akɛ wɔhi shi kɛya naanɔ .
Yɛ anɔkwale mli lɛ , Biblia lɛ kɛɔ akɛ , “ eŋɔ naanɔ hu ewo amɛtsui mli . ” ​ — Jajelɔ 3 : 11 .
Shi anɔkwa sane ji akɛ , adesai ehiii shi kɛyaaa naanɔ .
Agbɛnɛ hu lɛ , ani Nyɔŋmɔ efee nɔ ko koni ekɛtsu shihilɛ lɛ he nii ?
Hetoi ni Biblia lɛ kɛhãa lɛ hãa mɔ tsui nyɔɔ emli , ni ehãa wɔnaa nɔ hewɔ ni Yesu na amanehulu ní egbo lɛ .
Klɛŋklɛŋ yitsei etɛ ni yɔɔ Mose Klɛŋklɛŋ Wolo lɛ mli lɛ hãa wɔleɔ akɛ , Nyɔŋmɔ bɔ klɛŋklɛŋ nuu kɛ yoo lɛ , ni ji Adam kɛ Hawa , kɛ gbɛkpamɔ lɛ akɛ amɛbaahi shi kɛya naanɔ , ni etsɔɔ amɛ nɔ ni esa akɛ amɛfee koni amɛnyɛ amɛhi shi kɛya naanɔ .
Nakai yitsei lɛ tsɔɔ bɔ ni amɛbooo Nyɔŋmɔ toi ni no hã gbɛkpamɔ akɛ amɛbaahi shi kɛya naanɔ lɛ ŋmɛɛ amɛ .
Bɔ ni awie sane lɛ ahã lɛ yɛ mlɛo ​ — eyɛ mlɛo aahu akɛ mɛi komɛi susuɔ akɛ eji adesã .
Shi ana akɛ , saji ni yɔɔ Mose Klɛŋklɛŋ Wolo lɛ mli lɛ ji yinɔsane ko ni ja jogbaŋŋ , taakɛ eji yɛ Sanekpakpai lɛ agbɛfaŋ lɛ .
Mɛni ejɛ Adam toigbele lɛ mli kɛba ?
Biblia lɛ hãa hetoo akɛ : “ Gbɔmɔ kome [ Adam ] nɔ esha tsɔ kɛba je lɛ mli , ni gbele tsɔ esha nɔ kɛba , ni no hã gbele tsɛŋe gbɔmɛi fɛɛ , ejaakɛ amɛ fɛɛ amɛfee esha . ”
No hewɔ lɛ , gbɛkpamɔ akɛ ebaahi shi kɛya naanɔ lɛ ŋmɛɛ lɛ , ni yɛ naagbee lɛ , egbo .
Akɛni eshwiei ji wɔ hewɔ lɛ , esha ni efee lɛ ebatsɔ wɔgboshinii .
Shi ani Nyɔŋmɔ efee nɔ ko koni ekɛtsu shihilɛ lɛ he nii ?
Hɛɛ , Nyɔŋmɔ to gbɛjianɔ koni ekpɔ̃ , loo ehe nɔ ni ŋmɛɛ Adam shwiei lɛ , ni ji gbɛkpamɔ akɛ amɛbaahi shi kɛya naanɔ lɛ , ekoŋŋ .
Biblia lɛ kɛɔ yɛ Romabii 6 : 23 lɛ akɛ : “ Esha dɛŋ nyɔmɔwoo ji gbele . ”
Enɛ tsɔɔ akɛ , esha kɛ gbele baa .
Nakai nɔŋŋ wɔ hu wɔfeɔ esha , no hewɔ lɛ wɔwoɔ esha he nyɔmɔ , ni no ji gbele .
Shi afɔ wɔ awo nɛkɛ esha shihilɛ nɛɛ mli , ní jeee wɔ wɔfee .
No hewɔ lɛ , Nyɔŋmɔ jɛ suɔmɔ mli etsu e - Bi , Yesu , koni ebawo ‘ esha lɛ he nyɔmɔ ’ lɛ ehã wɔ .
Yesu gbele lɛ gbeleɔ gbɛ kɛhãa adesai koni amɛhi shi yɛ miishɛɛ mli kɛya naanɔ
Akɛni gbɔmɔ kome Adam , ni ji nuu ni eye emuu lɛ toigbele nɔ tsɔ ni wɔná esha kɛ gbele hewɔ lɛ , ehe bahia ni aná nuu ko ni eye emuu ní baafee toiboo kɛya gbele mli tɔ̃ɔ po , koni ebajie wɔ kɛjɛ nakai nyɔŋyeli lɛ shishi .
Biblia lɛ tsɔɔ mli yɛ nɛkɛ gbɛ nɔ akɛ : “ Bɔ ni gbɔmɔ kome lɛ toigbele lɛ hã mɛi pii tsɔmɔ eshafeelɔi lɛ , nakai nɔŋŋ hu gbɔmɔ kome lɛ toiboo lɛ baahã mɛi pii atsɔmɔ jalɔi . ”
Eshi ŋwɛi , ebatsɔ adesa ni eye emuu , * ni ebagbo ehã wɔ .
Enɛ hewɔ lɛ , wɔbaanyɛ wɔná shidaamɔ kpakpa yɛ Nyɔŋmɔ hiɛ , kɛ hiɛnɔkamɔ akɛ wɔbaahi shi kɛya naanɔ .
Shi mɛni hewɔ kwraa ehe bahia ni Yesu agbo yɛ yiŋtoo nɛɛ hewɔ lɛ ?
Ani kulɛ Nyɔŋmɔ Ofe lɛ nyɛŋ efã koni Adam shwiei lɛ ahi shi kɛya naanɔ ?
Eji Nyɔŋmɔ yeee jalɛ sane yɛ sane nɛɛ mli kulɛ , mɛi komɛi ayiŋ baafee amɛ kɔshikɔshi kɛji ebaaye jalɛ sane yɛ saji krokomɛi hu amli .
Akɛ nɔkwɛmɔnɔ lɛ , ani ebaaye jalɛ sane kɛ́ eehala Adam shwiei lɛ ateŋ mɛi ni esa akɛ amɛhi shi kɛya naanɔ ?
Ani abaanyɛ amu afɔ̃ enɔ akɛ ebaaye eshiwoi anɔ ?
Bɔ ni Nyɔŋmɔ ye jalɛ sane yɛ gbɛjianɔ ni eto koni ekpɔ̃ adesai lɛ mli lɛ maa nɔ mi kɛhãa wɔ akɛ ebaafee nɔ ni ja be fɛɛ be .
Nyɔŋmɔ tsɔ Yesu afɔleshaa gbele lɛ nɔ egbele gbɛ ehã adesai koni amɛhi shi yɛ Paradeiso yɛ shikpɔŋ lɛ nɔ kɛya naanɔ .
Kadimɔ nɔ ni Yesu wie yɛ Yohane 3 : 16 lɛ , ekɛɛ akɛ : “ Nyɔŋmɔ sumɔ je lɛ jogbaŋŋ aahu akɛ eŋɔ e - Bi koome lɛ ehã , koni mɔ fɛɛ mɔ ni jieɔ hemɔkɛyeli kpo yɛ emli lɛ hiɛ akakpãtã shi moŋ ená naanɔ wala . ”
No hewɔ lɛ , Yesu gbele lɛ tsɔɔ bɔ ni Nyɔŋmɔ yeɔ jalɛ sane , kɛ nɔ ni fe fɛɛ lɛ , etsɔɔ suɔmɔ kpele ni eyɔɔ kɛhã adesai .
Shi mɛni hewɔ esa akɛ Yesu ana amanehulu ni egbo piŋmɔ gbele , taakɛ atsɔɔ yɛ Sanekpakpai lɛ amli lɛ ?
Akɛni Yesu tee nɔ eye anɔkwa yɛ kaa ni naa wa fe fɛɛ ni etsɔ mli lɛ mli hewɔ lɛ , ehã ana faŋŋ akɛ , nɔ ni Abonsam wie akɛ kɛ́ adesai kɛ kaa kpe lɛ amɛyeŋ Nyɔŋmɔ anɔkwa lɛ ji amale .
Be ni Satan hã Adam , ní no mli lɛ eye emuu lɛ fee esha lɛ , ebaafee tamɔ nɔ ni Satan wiemɔ lɛ ji anɔkwale .
Shi Yesu ​ — mɔ ni eye emuu tamɔ Adam lɛ ​ — tee nɔ eye anɔkwa yɛ piŋmɔ ni naa wa ni ekɛkpe lɛ fɛɛ sɛɛ .
No hewɔ lɛ , ehã ana akɛ eji Adam hu miisumɔ ni eye Nyɔŋmɔ anɔkwa kulɛ , ebaanyɛ efee nakai .
Anɔkwa ni Yesu tee nɔ eye yɛ kaa mli lɛ ji nɔkwɛmɔnɔ kpakpa kɛhã wɔ .
Nyɔŋmɔ juro e - Bi Yesu yɛ toi ni ebo lɛ lɛ hewɔ , ni ehã lɛ wala ni fiteee yɛ ŋwɛi .
Yesu tsɔɔ nɔ ni esa akɛ wɔfee ; ewie akɛ : “ Enɛ ji naanɔ wala lɛ , akɛ amɛbaale bo , anɔkwa Nyɔŋmɔ kome lɛ , kɛ Yesu Kristo , mɔ ni otsu lɛ lɛ . ” ​ — Yohane 17 : 3 .
Wɔmiiwo bo hewalɛ ní okase Yehowa , ni ji anɔkwa Nyɔŋmɔ lɛ , kɛ Yesu Kristo , ni ji e - Bi lɛ he nii babaoo .
Yehowa Odasefoi ni yɔɔ he ni oyɔɔ lɛ baasumɔ ni amɛye amɛbua bo .
Agbɛnɛ hu kɛ́ otee wɔ - wɛb saiti , ni ji www.jw.org / gaa lɛ , obaaná saji babaoo ni baaye abua bo .
Kwɛmɔ sane ni ji , “ The Historical Character of Genesis , ” ni yɔɔ Insight on the Scriptures , Kpo 1 , ni Yehowa Odasefoi fee lɛ baafa 922 lɛ .
Nyɔŋmɔ jie e - Bi lɛ wala kɛjɛ ŋwɛi kɛbawo Maria fɔmɔ kotoku lɛ mli , ni enɛ hã ená musu , ni Nyɔŋmɔ mumɔ krɔŋkrɔŋ lɛ bu Yesu he koni ekaná esha ko kɛjɛ Maria dɛŋ . ​ — Luka 1 : 31 , 35 .
Gbi gbɛkɛ dani enɔ jetsɛremɔ lɛ Yesu kɛ ewala baafɔ̃ shi lɛ , ebua ebɔfoi anɔkwafoi lɛ anaa ni eto egbele lɛ Kaimɔ lɛ shishi .
Ekɛɛ amɛ akɛ : “ Nyɛyaa nɔ nyɛfea enɛ kɛkaia mi . ”
Yehowa Odasefoi ni yɔɔ jeŋ fɛɛ lɛ boɔ famɔ nɛɛ toi , no hewɔ lɛ , daa afi lɛ amɛbuaa amɛhe naa kɛkaiɔ Yesu gbele lɛ .
Afi nɛɛ , abaaye Yesu gbele lɛ Kaimɔ lɛ Shɔ , March 23 , be ni hulu enyɔ shi .
Aheee shika ; ni anyɛŋ onɔ ni otsu onia .
Ofainɛ bi Yehowa Odasefoi ni yɔɔ okutso lɛ mli lɛ ni amɛtsɔɔ bo be kɛ he ni abaafee yɛ .
