Abonsam kɛ Yesu gba sane ni ‘ eka ’ lɛ .
Kulɛ Abonsam ji ŋwɛibɔfo ko ni yɔɔ krɔŋkrɔŋ , shi “ edamɔɔɔ shi shiŋŋ yɛ anɔkwale lɛ mli . ”
Ebatsɔ amalelɔ , ni etse Nyɔŋmɔ hiɛ atua .
Ŋwɛibɔfoi krokomɛi yafata Satan he kɛtse atua lɛ . ​ — Kpojiemɔ 12 : 9 .
Abonsam eshwila mɛi pii koni amɛkahe amɛye akɛ eyɛ shihilɛ mli . ​ — 2 Korintobii 4 : 4 .
MƐI KOMƐI KƐƆ akɛ eji amale akɛ Abonsam baanyɛ ekudɔ mɛi , ni mɛi komɛi hu sheɔ gbeyei akɛ mumɔi fɔji baanyɛ akudɔ amɛ .
Abonsam náa adesai anɔ hewalɛ waa diɛŋtsɛ , shi jeee adesai fɛɛ ekudɔɔ .
Abonsam tsɔɔ ŋaa gbɛ nɔ elakaa mɛi koni enine ashɛ mɛi babaoo nɔ . ​ — 2 Korintobii 11 : 14 .
Mumɔi fɔji baanyɛ akudɔ mɛi bei komɛi . — Mateo 12 : 22 .
Nyɔŋmɔ baanyɛ eye ebua bo ni ‘ otsĩ Abonsam ’ gbɛ kwraa . ​ — Yakobo 4 : 7 .
Wɔ fɛɛ wɔtɔ̃ɔ , ni wɔtɔmɔi lɛ baanyɛ agba mɛi krokomɛi anaa .
