Wɔsɛɛ lɛ , mɛɛ gbɛ nɔ “ gwantɛŋi krokomɛi ” lɛ baaná Yehowa duromɔ lɛ he sɛɛ ?
Yehowa baatee mɛi akpekpei abɔ ni náaa amɛle lɛ dani amɛgboi lɛ hu shi .
Yohane ŋma akɛ : “ Mina gbohii lɛ , mɛi wuji kɛ mɛi bibii , damɔ maŋtsɛ sɛi lɛ hiɛ , ni agbele wolokpoi anaa .
Adamɔ nibii ni aŋmala yɛ wolokpoi lɛ amli lɛ anɔ akojo gbohii lɛ yɛ amɛnifeemɔi lɛ anaa .
Ni ŋshɔ lɛ jie gbohii ni yɔɔ emli lɛ ehã , ni gbele kɛ Gbonyo Bu lɛ jie gbohii ni yɔɔ amɛmli lɛ amɛhã , ni akojo amɛteŋ mɔ fɛɛ mɔ yɛ enifeemɔi lɛ anaa . ”

Biblia lɛ kɛɔ akɛ : “ Abaahã bɔɔ nii lɛ diɛŋtsɛ hu aye amɛhe kɛjɛ fitemɔ nyɔŋyeli mli ní amɛná Nyɔŋmɔ bii lɛ anunyam heyeli lɛ . ” Yehowa mli hi waa .
Esaa ekɛɛ : “ Ŋmaa , ejaakɛ wiemɔi nɛɛ yɛ mli , ni anɔkwale ni . ”
Kɛ́ wɔkɛ ekãa shiɛ sane kpakpa nɛɛ wɔhã mɛi krokomɛi lɛ , no tsɔɔ akɛ , wɔmiijie Yehowa yi yɛ eduromɔ lɛ hewɔ !
