Mɛni baanyɛ aba mɛi ni kɛ amɛhewalɛ fɛɛ tiuɔ heloonaa nibii asɛɛ lɛ anɔ ?
Mɛni he wɔbaasusu ? Ni mɛɛ gbɛ nɔ ebaaye ebua wɔ ?
8 , 9 . ( a ) Mɛni hewɔ esaaa akɛ wɔyeɔ wɔtsui tuutu yɛ wɔhiamɔ nii ahe lɛ ?
