[ 1 ] ( kuku 14 ) Kwɛmɔ wolo ni ji Nyɔŋmɔ Maŋtsɛyeli lɛ Ebɔi Nɔyeli !
Kaakwɛkwɛɛ ohe , shi mi ji o - Nyɔŋmɔ lɛ !
Yɛ kpee lɛ shishi lɛ , nyɛmi nuu ko bi mi kɛji masumɔ ni mashiɛ .
Nyɛmi yoo ko kɛ mi kɛ gbekɛbii krokomɛi ni baa jɛmɛ lɛ bɔi Biblia lɛ kasemɔ kɛtsɔ wolo ni ji The Harp of God lɛ nɔ , ni minya nibii ni mikaseɔ lɛ ahe waa .
Be ni wɔyaa lɛ , wɔho osɔfo ko he ni miwie akɛ : “ Abotiai lɛ eko ni yaa yɛ jɛmɛ lɛ . ”
Nyɛmi nuu lɛ hã wɔyi shi kɛjɛ baisiko lɛ nɔ wɔyata tso ko ni afó afɔ̃ shi lɛ nɔ , ni ebi mi akɛ : “ Namɔ hã bo hegbɛ akɛ okojo mɛi ni otsɛ amɛ abotiai ?
Esa akɛ wɔhiɛ asɔ hegbɛ ni ahã wɔ akɛ wɔshiɛ sane kpakpa lɛ , ni wɔshi kojomɔ lɛ wɔhã Yehowa . ”
Nyɛmi nuu onukpa kroko hã mina akɛ , bei komɛi lɛ , dani wɔbaaná miishɛɛ ni jɛɔ nɔhamɔ mli kɛbaa lɛ , esa akɛ wɔto wɔtsui shi yɛ shihilɛi ni jaraa amli .
Eŋa lɛ batsɔ nyɛmi .
No mli lɛ , mije gbɛgbamɔ nitsumɔ lɛ shishi etsɛko
Anɔkwa , osɔfoi lɛ hã ashwie mɛi ni he wɔwoji lɛ eko lɛ kɛje amɛnitsumɔi amli , ni amɛhã afã wɔ kɛjɛ he ni wɔyato lɛ .
Miyako ŋshɔ hiɛ dã , no hewɔ lɛ mimii shɛ mihe waa .
Wɔkɛ afii enumɔ shiɛ yɛ ŋshɔkpɔi bibii nɛɛ anɔ , titri lɛ yɛ hei ni etse amɛhe banee ni Odasefonyo ko kwraa bɛ lɛ .
Maŋsɛɛ sɔɔlɔi ni tsu nii yɛ Sibia lɛlɛ lɛ mli ( kɛjɛ abɛku kɛmiiya ninejurɔgbɛ ) : Ron Parkin , Dick Ryde , Gust Maki , kɛ Stanley Carter
Bei pii lɛ , amɛhãa wɔ loo ŋmɔŋ , paya , kɛ ŋkatiɛ .
Kɛ́ shɛ gbɛkɛ lɛ , wɔtswaa lɛlɛ lɛ ŋmɛlɛ lɛ ni mɛi lɛ baa .
Amɛteŋ mɛi komɛi kɛ hiɛdɔɔ tsu sɔ̃ nɛɛ he nii , ni ehã wɔmii shɛ wɔhe waa .
Be ni wɔyashɛ lɛ , mikɛ nyɛmi yoo maŋsɛɛ sɔɔlɔ ko ni he yɔɔ fɛo ni atsɛɔ lɛ Maxine Boyd lɛ kpe , ni mitsui mɔ lɛ .
No hewɔ lɛ , mikɛɛ mihe akɛ , ‘ Ronald , kɛ́ oosumɔ oblayoo nɛɛ lɛ , belɛ kaashwɛ yɛ kpãa nɔ . ’
Otsii etɛ sɛɛ lɛ , mibi lɛ suɔmɔ , ni ekpɛlɛ .
Ahã mi kɛ Maxine sɔmɔ akɛ maŋsɛɛ sɔɔlɔi yɛ Puerto Rico , no hewɔ lɛ mináaa maku misɛɛ kɛya ŋshɔkpɔi lɛ anɔ dɔŋŋ .
Akɛ nɔkwɛmɔnɔ lɛ , yɛ akrowa ko ni atsɛɔ lɛ Potala Pastillo lɛ mli lɛ , no mli lɛ Odasefoi awekui enyɔ komɛi kɛ amɛbii babaoo yɛ jɛmɛ , ni kɛ́ efee lɛ miyakpãa bɛlɛ mihãa amɛ .
Mibi gbekɛbii lɛ ateŋ mɔ kome ni atsɛɔ lɛ Hilda lɛ kɛji ebaasumɔ ni ekɛ wɔ aya shiɛmɔ .
No hewɔ lɛ , wɔhe tokota wɔhã lɛ , ni efata wɔhe kɛtee shiɛmɔ .
Be ni wɔtee lɛ , nyɛmi yoo ko ni egbe Gilead Skul lɛ naa lɛ tsi ebɛŋkɛ wɔ , ni ekɛɛ wɔ akɛ : “ Mile akɛ nyɛkaiŋ mi .
Miji gbekɛ yoo fioo lɛ ni bɛ tokota , ni nyɛkɛkpe yɛ Pastillo lɛ . ”
Shishijee mli lɛ , mi kɛ Lennart Johnson ni tsu nitsumɔ lɛ fã kpotoo .
No mli lɛ , Nathan Knorr ji mɔ ni nyiɛ Yehowa Odasefoi lɛ ahiɛ , ni eba Puerto Rico .
Sɛɛ mli lɛ , ekɛ mi wie waa ni ewo mi ŋaa ni mikase bɔ ni atoɔ nibii ahe gbɛjianɔ jogbaŋŋ .
Nakai beiaŋ fɛɛ lɛ , mimami kã he eji Odasefonyo , shi mipapa bɛ anɔkwale lɛ mli .
Yɛ afi 2011 lɛ , misuɔlɔ Maxine gbo .
Miishwe waa ni mikɛ lɛ akpe ekoŋŋ be ni atee lɛ shi kɛba wala mli lɛ .
No mli lɛ mihi ŋshɔkpɔ nɛɛ nɔ afii 60 sɔŋŋ , ni minu he tamɔ nɔ ni mibatsɔ jɛmɛ nyo .
Mɛi ni baa miŋɔɔ lɛ ateŋ mɛi komɛi kɛ mi basusuɔ amɛ diɛŋtsɛ amɛnaagbai aloo amɛweku mli naagbai ahe .
Ekɔɔɔ he eko he ni wɔsɔmɔɔ Yehowa yɛ lɛ , wɔbaanyɛ wɔya nɔ wɔjie eyi .
Leonard Smith wala shihilɛ he sane yɛ April 15 , 2012 Buu - Mɔɔ lɛ mli .
