No hewɔ lɛ , mifã miyahi mibihii lɛ ateŋ mɔ kome kɛ eŋa masɛi .
Mɛni wɔbaanyɛ wɔfee koni suɔmɔ ni wɔyɔɔ kɛhã Yehowa lɛ he akajɔ ?
Mɛɛ gbɛ nɔ wɔbaanyɛ wɔhã suɔmɔ ni wɔyɔɔ kɛhã anɔkwalei ni wɔkase yɛ Biblia lɛ mli lɛ mli awa ?
Mɛni hewɔ ehe miihia ni wɔsumɔ wɔnyɛmimɛi lɛ ?
Amɛtee nɔ amɛkɛ ekãa ‘ jaje Kristo lɛ he sane kpakpa lɛ . ’
Ŋmɛnɛ lɛ , suɔmɔ ni mɛi yɔɔ kɛhã Nyɔŋmɔ lɛ he ejɔ , ni ehe miiya nɔ eejɔ lolo .
Suɔmɔ Yehowa ( Kwɛmɔ kuku 10 )
( Kanemɔ Lala 119 : 97 - 100 . )
Suɔmɔ Biblia mli anɔkwalei lɛ ( Kwɛmɔ kuku 14 )
Gbi gbɛkɛ ni enɔ jetsɛremɔ lɛ abaagbe Yesu lɛ , ekɛɛ ekaselɔi lɛ akɛ : “ Miihã nyɛ kitã hee akɛ nyɛsumɔsumɔa nyɛhe ; bɔ ni misumɔ nyɛ lɛ , nyɛ hu nyɛsumɔsumɔa nyɛhe nakai nɔŋŋ .
Kɛji nyɛsumɔɔ nyɛhe lɛ , no mɛi fɛɛ kɛbaale akɛ mikaselɔi ji nyɛ . ” ​ — Yoh . 13 : 34 , 35 .
Bɔfo Yohane ŋma akɛ : “ Mɔ ni sumɔɔɔ enyɛmi ní enaa lɛ lɛ , enyɛŋ esumɔ Nyɔŋmɔ ní enaaa lɛ lɛ . ”
Suɔmɔ onyɛmimɛi Kristofoi lɛ ( Kwɛmɔ kuku 17 )
Mɛni ji nibii komɛi ni wɔbaanyɛ wɔfee kɛtsɔɔ akɛ wɔsumɔɔ wɔnyɛmimɛi lɛ ?
Kanemɔ 1 Tesalonikabii 4 : 9 , 10 .
21 : 15 .
Be ni amɛfee nakai lɛ , amɛgbe loi pii , “ shi loi lɛ afalɛ hewɔ lɛ , amɛnyɛɛɛ yaa lɛ amɛgbala . ” ​ — Yoh .
21 : 1 - 6 .
( b ) Mɛɛ nɔ ko ni he hiaa waa nyɛmi nuu ko ni yɔɔ Thailand lɛ yɔse yɛ nitsumɔ ni etsuɔ be ko ni eho lɛ he ?
Shi ehe mibe fɛɛ , ni enɛ hewɔ lɛ , be fioo ko pɛ mináa kɛhãa mumɔŋ nibii .
Naagbee lɛ , miyɔse akɛ , dani manyɛ mikɛ Maŋtsɛyeli lɛ aye klɛŋklɛŋ gbɛhe lɛ , esa akɛ matsake nitsumɔ ni mitsuɔ lɛ . ”
Ewie akɛ : “ Mikɛ aaafee afi kome to minibii ahe gbɛjianɔ .
Kɛkɛ ni mikpɛ miyiŋ akɛ mahɔ̃ɔ ais krim yɛ gbɛ lɛ he .
Kɛ́ mikɛ mɛi ni be ko ni eho lɛ mikɛtsuɔ nii lɛ kpe lɛ , amɛŋmɔɔ mi , ni amɛbiɔ mi nɔ hewɔ ni miisumɔ ni mahɔ̃ɔ ais krim moŋ fe ni mata ɛɛkɔndishiŋ mli ni masaa kɔmpiutai .
Misɔle mibi Yehowa ni eye ebua mi koni manyɛ makpee shihilɛ lɛ naa ni mashɛ oti ni mikɛma mihiɛ lɛ he , no ji , ni maná be babaoo kɛhã mumɔŋ nibii .
Mihe basa kɛ ais krim lɛ feemɔ , ni mɛi nya he waa .
Etsɛɛɛ ni jara lɛ baŋɔɔ aahu akɛ , abɔ ni mafee lɛ , mihɔ̃ɔ fɛɛ dani je naa .
Anɔkwa , shika ni miná kɛjɛ ais krim lɛ mli lɛ fa fe nɔ ni miná kɛjɛ kɔmpiutai asaamɔ lɛ mli .
Mifeee yeyeeye tamɔ tsutsu be ni misaa kɔmpiutai lɛ , ni enɛ ehã miná miishɛɛ fe be ko ni eho .
Nɔ ni fe fɛɛ lɛ , amrɔ nɛɛ minuɔ he akɛ wekukpaa ni yɔɔ mi kɛ Yehowa teŋ lɛ mli ewa waa . ” ​ — Kanemɔ Mateo 5 : 3 , 6 .
Ebaptisimɔ lɛ sɛɛ lɛ , ewie akɛ : “ Nɔ pɛ ni dɔɔ mi ji akɛ , mifite be babaoo dani miyɔse akɛ , kɛ́ mɔ ko sɔmɔ Yehowa lɛ , miishɛɛ ni mɔ lɛ náa lɛ da kwraa fe miishɛɛ ni enáa kɛji etiu nibii ni mɛi kɛjieɔ amɛhiɛtserɛ yɛ je nɛɛ mli lɛ asɛɛ . ”
Yesu kɛɛ “ mɔ ko nyɛŋ atsɔ nyɔŋ ehã nuŋtsɔmɛi enyɔ . ”
Kɛkɛ ni ekɛfata he akɛ : “ Nyɛnyɛŋ nyɛtsɔmɔ nyɔji nyɛhã Nyɔŋmɔ kɛ Ninámɔ fɛɛ . ”
( Kanemɔ 1 Korintobii 2 : 14 . )
Kwɛmɔ sane ni yitso ji , “ Ani Hiɛtserɛjiemɔi ni Ohalaa lɛ Ahe yɛ Sɛɛnamɔ ? ”
Agbɛnɛ hu , wɔfɔɔ shiɛmɔ yaa . ”
Edɔ wɔ waa akɛ wɔbaashi wɔ - Biblia mli nikaselɔi lɛ . ”
Shi nyɔɔŋ kome sɛɛ lɛ , amɛnu sane kpakpa ko .
Miriam wie akɛ : “ Ahã wɔle akɛ , abaasumɔ ni wɔsɔmɔ yɛ jɛmɛ akɛ gbɛgbalɔi krɛdɛi .
Wɔmii shɛ wɔhe waa akɛ wɔbaaya nɔ wɔhi Panama ! ”
Amɛkɛ amɛhiɛ fɔ̃ shiwoo ni yɔɔ Lala 37 : 5 lɛ nɔ . Jɛmɛ kɛɔ akɛ : “ Gbɛ ní onyiɛ nɔ lɛ , ŋɔɔfɔ̃ Yehowa nɔ , ní oŋɔ ohiɛ hu ofɔ̃ enɔ , ni eeefee . ”
Ŋmɛnɛ lɛ , wɔhã wɔshihilɛ efee mlɛo , shi nɔ ko nɔ ko bɛ ni he hiaa wɔ lɛɛlɛŋ ni wɔnáaa . ”
Mɛni hewɔ esaaa akɛ efeɔ wɔ naakpɛɛ akɛ wɔkɛ shihilɛi ni jaraa baakpe yɛ wɔgbalashihilɛ kɛ wɔweku lɛ mli ?
Wɔle akɛ , Yehowa miisumɔ ni ahi ahã wɔ , tamɔ bɔ ni eshwe ehã etsuji ni hi shi yɛ blema lɛ . ​ — Kanemɔ Yeremia 29 : 11 , 12 .
( Kanemɔ 1 Samuel 1 : 4 - 7 . )
Paula wie akɛ : “ Eyɛ mli akɛ Ann jeee miwekunyo moŋ , shi bɔ ni ejie suɔmɔ kpo etsɔɔ mi ni esusu mihe lɛ ye ebua mi waa .
Eye ebua mi koni maya nɔ masɔmɔ Yehowa . ”
( Kanemɔ Lala 145 : 18 , 19 . )
“ He ni nyɛjwetri yɔɔ lɛ , jɛmɛ nyɛtsuii hu baahi . ” — LUKA 12 : 34 .
Be ni wɔsusuɔ saji nɛɛ ahe lɛ , kwɛmɔ nɔ ni bo akɛ mɔ aŋkro lɛ , obaanyɛ ofee koni suɔmɔ ni oyɔɔ kɛhã mumɔŋ jwetrii nɛɛ mli awa waa .
Ani oona bɔ ni adiagba nɛɛ jara wa hã nuu nɛɛ ?
( Kanemɔ Marko 10 : 28 - 30 . )
( a ) Mɛni hewɔ bɔfo Paulo wie akɛ shiɛmɔ nitsumɔ lɛ ji ‘ jwetri ni akɛwo sũ nii amli ’ lɛ ?
( Kanemɔ Romabii 1 : 14 , 15 ; 2 Timoteo 4 : 2 . )
Amɛteŋ mɛi komɛi miisɔmɔ yɛ Betel , ni mɛi komɛi hu miisɔmɔ akɛ gbɛgbalɔi kɛ asafoŋ onukpai .
Irene wie akɛ , “ Eji mitiu nibii krokomɛi asɛɛ kulɛ , mikpaaa shi akɛ maná miishɛɛ waa nɛkɛ . ”
Mɛni ji ‘ jwetritoohe ’ ni Yesu wie he yɛ Mateo 13 : 52 lɛ ? Ni te wɔbaafee tɛŋŋ wɔkɛ nibii ato jɛmɛ ?
( Kanemɔ Abɛi 2 : 4 - 7 . )
Susumɔ niiashikpamɔ ko ni nyɛmi nuu ko ni atsɛɔ lɛ Peter lɛ ná lɛ he okwɛ .
Ebi lɛ akɛ , “ No hewɔ lɛ , mibinuu , mɛɛ wiemɔ mli aŋma Daniel wolo lɛ yɛ ? ”
Be ni mishɛ shĩa ni mikwɛ Buu - Mɔɔ kɛ Awake !
ni eba yɛ nyɔji ni tsɔ hiɛ lɛ amli lɛ , mina sane ko ni awie yɛ mli akɛ aŋma Daniel wolo lɛ yɛ Aramaik mli . ”
Kɛ́ ofee nakai lɛ , ‘ obaabɔ jwetri yɛ ŋwɛi , he ni julɔ ko bɛŋkɛɛɛ , ni omlɛ̃gɛ̃ ko hu kpeee nii yɛ lɛ .
Ejaakɛ he ni ojwetri yɔɔ lɛ , jɛmɛ otsui hu baahi . ’ ​ — Luka 12 : 33 , 34 .
“ No mli lɛ , minyɛɛɛ mi kɛ nyɛmi nuu ko ni mikɛtsuɔ nii lɛ ahi shi yɛ toiŋjɔlɛ mli .
Gbi ko be ni wɔbolɔɔ wɔwoɔ wɔhe lɛ , mɛi enyɔ bati wɔbéi lɛ nɔ . ” ​ — CHRIS .
“ Nyɛmi yoo ko ni mikɛ lɛ fɔɔ shiɛmɔ yaa lɛ kɛ mi kpa yaa trukaa .
Misusu he aahu , shi mijwɛŋmɔ shɛɛɛ he . ” ​ — JANET .
“ Be ko lɛ , mikɛ mɛi enyɔ miigba sane yɛ fon nɔ ni amɛteŋ mɔ kome kɛ wɔ ye shɛɛ .
Misusu akɛ eshi kpãa lɛ nɔ , no hewɔ lɛ , miwie nibii gbohii yɛ ehe mitsɔɔ mɔ kroko lɛ .
Shi asomoaŋ , eshiko kpãa lɛ nɔ . ” ​ — MICHAEL .
