Mɛni hewɔ esoro bɔ ni Abner fee enii yɛ David he lɛ kwraa yɛ bɔ ni Yonatan fee enii yɛ ehe lɛ he ?
Tsĩi sui ni baanyɛ aye abua wɔ ni wɔye Nyɔŋmɔ anɔkwa lɛ atã , ni otsɔɔ gbɛ ni amɛteŋ eko fɛɛ eko baanyɛ aye abua wɔ .
Mɛni David fee kɛtsɔɔ akɛ eyeɔ Nyɔŋmɔ anɔkwa ?
( a ) Mɛni hewɔ wɔbaanyɛ wɔkɛɛ akɛ David ye Nyɔŋmɔ anɔkwa lɛ ?
( b ) Yɛ David sɛɛ lɛ , namɛi hu ahe wɔbaasusu yɛ nikasemɔ nɛɛ mli ?
Mɛni wɔkaseɔ kɛjɛɔ Abishai sane lɛ mli ?
Yɛ wɔfɔmɔsu naa lɛ , wɔyeɔ wɔnanemɛi , wɔwekumɛi , kɛ mɛi krokomɛi ni wɔsumɔɔ lɛ anɔkwa .
Ni mɛni efee kɛtsɔɔ akɛ eyeɔ Nyɔŋmɔ anɔkwa ?
Mɛɛ sui baaye abua wɔ ni wɔye Nyɔŋmɔ anɔkwa ?
Mɛni wɔkaseɔ kɛjɛɔ Abner , Absalom , kɛ Baruk sane lɛ mli ?
Ni bo lɛ nii wuji otaoɔ ohã ohe ?
Gbaa niiashikpamɔ ko ni hãa wɔnaa akɛ , wɔnyɛŋ wɔye Nyɔŋmɔ anɔkwa kɛji akɛ wɔsusuɔ wɔ pɛ wɔhe .
Daniel wie akɛ : “ Eye ebua mi ni mibana akɛ , kɛ́ miitao maye Nyɔŋmɔ anɔkwa lɛ , belɛ esa akɛ makpa oblayoo lɛ ŋmaa .
Be ni David fee esha lɛ , mɛni Natan fee kɛtsɔɔ akɛ eyeɔ Nyɔŋmɔ kɛ David fɛɛ anɔkwa ?
Kɛ́ oye Yehowa anɔkwa lɛ , mɛɛ gbɛ nɔ no baaye abua bo ni ojie mlihilɛ kpo otsɔɔ onanemɛi kɛ owekumɛi , ni oye amɛ anɔkwa ?
Mɛni hewɔ ebi ni Hushai aná ekãa koni enyɛ eye Nyɔŋmɔ anɔkwa lɛ ?
Kɛ́ wɔmiitao wɔye Nyɔŋmɔ anɔkwa lɛ , mɛni hewɔ ebiɔ ni wɔfee ekãa lɛ ?
Misɔle ni Nyɔŋmɔ ahã mafee ekãa , ni mikatsake mijwɛŋmɔ yɛ gbɛ ni mikɔ lɛ he .
Amrɔ nɛɛ , nibii amli ejɔ fioo , ni minyɛɔ miyasaraa amɛ kpitiokpitio . ” ​ — Kanemɔ Abɛi 29 : 25 .
