Yesu hã lɛ hetoo akɛ : “ Esa akɛ osumɔ Yehowa o - Nyɔŋmɔ lɛ kɛ otsui muu fɛɛ kɛ osusuma muu fɛɛ kɛ ojwɛŋmɔ muu fɛɛ . ”
( Kanemɔ 2 Korintobii 5 : 14 , 15 ; 1 Yohane 4 : 9 , 19 . )
18 , 19 . ( a ) Mɛni hewɔ esaaa akɛ osheɔ gbeyei akɛ obaajɔɔ ohe nɔ ohã Yehowa ?
( b ) Mɛni hewɔ oshwaŋ ohe kɔkɔɔkɔ akɛ ojɔɔ ohe nɔ ohã Yehowa ?
