2 , 3 . ( a ) Mɛni hewɔ Biblia lɛ woko wɔ mlai yɛ shihilɛ mli nɔ fɛɛ nɔ he lɛ ?
Mɛɛ gbɛ nɔ yiŋ ni wɔkpɛɔ lɛ saa wɔ kɛ mɛi krokomɛi ahe ?
Kɛ́ wɔbaakpɛ yiŋ yɛ sane ko he , ni mla ko bɛ Biblia lɛ mli ni kɔɔ he lɛ , te wɔbaafee tɛŋŋ wɔna nɔ ni Yehowa miisumɔ ni wɔfee yɛ he ?
Te fee tɛŋŋ Yesu na nɔ ni Yehowa taoɔ ni efee ?
( Kanemɔ Mateo 4 : 2 - 4 . )
Kɛ́ wɔmiikane Biblia lɛ , loo wɔmiifee aŋkro nikasemɔ lɛ , mɛɛ saji wɔbaanyɛ wɔbi wɔhe ?
Mɛɛ gbɛ nɔ asafo lɛ woji kɛ asafoŋ kpeei baanyɛ aye abua wɔ ni wɔle Yehowa susumɔ yɛ saji srɔtoi ahe ?
Okɛ nɔkwɛmɔnɔ ahã kɛtsɔɔ nɔ hewɔ ni kɛ́ wɔle Yehowa susumɔ lɛ , ebaaye ebua wɔ ni wɔkpɛ yiŋ ni ja .
( Kanemɔ Luka 18 : 29 , 30 . )
Te obaafee tɛŋŋ ole kɛji atade ko ni otaoɔ owo lɛ baasa Yehowa hiɛ ?
( d ) Dani wɔbaakpɛ wɔyiŋ yɛ sane ko ni he hiaa waa lɛ he lɛ , mɛni esa akɛ wɔfee ?
( Kanemɔ 1 Mose 6 : 5 , 6 . )
Kɛ́ wɔkpɛ yiŋ ni sa Yehowa hiɛ lɛ , mɛɛ gbɛ nɔ wɔbaaná he sɛɛ ?
Wɔbaaya nɔ wɔkase nibii pii yɛ Yehowa he aahu kɛya naanɔ .
Yɛ wɔbaptisimɔ lɛ sɛɛ lɛ , mɛni hewɔ esa akɛ wɔya nɔ wɔfee tsakemɔi yɛ wɔshihilɛ mli ?
Mɛni hewɔ Yehowa miisumɔ ni wɔmia wɔhiɛ ni wɔye sui gbohii ni eka wɔhe lɛ anɔ lɛ ?
Kɛ́ wɔmiitao ni Nyɔŋmɔ Wiemɔ lɛ aya nɔ atsake wɔ lɛ , mɛni wɔbaanyɛ wɔfee ?
1 - 3 . ( a ) Mɛni ji sui komɛi ni ebaanyɛ ewa kɛhã mɛi ni abaptisi amɛ lɛ po akɛ amɛbaaye nɔ ?
( b ) Ni mɛɛ saji ekolɛ wɔbaabi wɔhe ?
Mɛni hewɔ wɔnyɛɛɛ wɔfee nɔ ni Yehowa sumɔɔ be fɛɛ be lɛ ?
Mɛɛ sui komɛi wɔkwa dani abaptisi wɔ ? Shi mɛni ji sui komɛi ni baanyɛ aya nɔ agba wɔnaa ?
6 , 7 . ( a ) Mɛɛ gbɛjianɔ Yehowa eto koni wɔnyɛ wɔkɛ lɛ abɔ naanyo yɛ emuu ni wɔyeee lɛ fɛɛ sɛɛ ?
( b ) Mɛni hewɔ esaaa akɛ wɔshashaoɔ shi kwraa akɛ wɔbaabi Yehowa dɛŋ eshaifaa ?
Mɛni hewɔ esa akɛ wɔya nɔ wɔtsake wɔjeŋba ni wɔwo subaŋ hee lɛ ?
Mɛɛ su baaye abua wɔ ni wɔkɛ nibii ni wɔkaseɔ yɛ Nyɔŋmɔ Wiemɔ lɛ mli lɛ atsu nii , ni wɔya nɔ wɔfee tsakemɔi ?
Mɛni hewɔ Yehowa miisumɔ ni wɔmia wɔhiɛ ni wɔye sui gbohii ni eka wɔhe lɛ anɔ lɛ ?
Mɛni kɛ́ wɔfee lɛ , ebaaye ebua wɔ ni wɔkase Yehowa jogbaŋŋ ni wɔjie esui lɛ akpo ?
( Kwɛmɔ akrabatsa ni ji , “ Biblia lɛ kɛ Sɔlemɔ Ye Ebua Amɛ ni Amɛtsake . ” )
Kɛ́ efee tamɔ nɔ ni eetɔ wɔ kɛ sui gbohii komɛi atsakemɔ lɛ , mɛni hewɔ esaaa akɛ wɔnijiaŋ jeɔ wui lɛ ?
Kɛ́ wɔye Yehowa anɔkwa lɛ , mɛɛ shihilɛ kpakpa wɔbaaná wɔsɛɛ ?
Mɛni hewɔ wɔbaanyɛ wɔná nɔmimaa akɛ , Biblia lɛ baanyɛ aya nɔ etsake wɔ lɛ ?
[ 1 ] ( kuku 1 ) Atsake gbɛ́i lɛ .
Russell : “ Nɔ ni ye ebua mi ji akɛ , mikɛ hiɛdɔɔ kpa Yehowa fai ni ewa mi , ni mikane Biblia lɛ daa gbi .
Mijwɛŋ wiemɔi ni yɔɔ 2 Petro 2 : 11 lɛ , kɛ ŋaa ni asafoŋ onukpai lɛ wo mi lɛ nɔ , ni no hu ye ebua mi waa . ”
Maria Victoria : “ Mikpa Yehowa fai waa ni eye ebua mi ni makpa mɛi ahe oshekuyeli .
Kɛfata he lɛ , mikɛ mɛi ni sumɔɔ mɛi ahe oshekuyeli lɛ ebɔɔɔ gbagbalii .
Lala 64 : 2 - 5 lɛ hã mina akɛ , kɛ́ mitsakeee lɛ , mɛi baasɔle ni Yehowa abaa amɛyi koni mikaye amɛ awui !
Mibayɔse hu akɛ , kɛ́ mitee nɔ miye mɛi ahe osheku lɛ , mifeŋ nɔkwɛmɔnɔ kpakpa mihaŋ mɛi krokomɛi , ni no baahã agbe Yehowa gbɛ́i lɛ he guɔ . ”
Linda : “ Mibɔ mɔdɛŋ akɛ male tratii lɛ eko fɛɛ eko mli sane jogbaŋŋ kɛ bɔ ni mafee ni mikɛhã .
Mikɛ mɛi ni sumɔɔ ni amɛtsɔ gbɛi srɔtoi anɔ amɛshiɛ lɛ bɔ , ni no eye ebua mi waa .
Ni miyaa nɔ misɔleɔ be fɛɛ be . ”
